data.description: Introducing this enchanting 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence located in the picturesque North Pole, Alaska. As you enter, you are greeted by a spacious and inviting living room.  The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, featuring elegant black granite countertops and modern appliances, ready to cater to all your cooking needs. Each bedroom in this home offers a tranquil space, bathed in natural light, promising restful nights and a serene ambiance.  The master suite is particularly noteworthy, offering a private bathroom, providing an exclusive and peaceful retreat. Venturing outside, the backyard presents a multitude of possibilities for outdoor activities and relaxation, set against the backdrop of Alaska's stunning natural scenery and a fenced in yard.  This property is situated in a welcoming community, offering more than just a home; it provides an experience of life surrounded by the unique beauty and tranquility of Alaska. Ideal for nature lovers, or those seeking a peaceful retreat, 2795 Benjamin Franklin is more than a residence – it's a gateway to a life immersed in the natural splendor of the North Pole.  This home is not just an address, it's a promise of a life filled with the wonder and charm inherent to one of the most magical places on Earth.
